1
00:01:10,919 --> 00:01:12,279
Did you access the files?

2
00:01:14,160 --> 00:01:15,120
Look, officer,

3
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:16,839
I've explained this to you many times.

4
00:01:17,440 --> 00:01:17,919
Oh, right.

5
00:01:18,319 --> 00:01:19,599
I have a friend who works here.

6
00:01:19,919 --> 00:01:20,680
Her name is Lin Yaoyao.

7
00:01:21,239 --> 00:01:22,519
Can you ask her to come talk to me?

8
00:01:22,519 --> 00:01:24,599
It's the same whether she or I question you.

9
00:01:24,839 --> 00:01:25,760
Even if she knows you,

10
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:26,720
and she were here right now,

11
00:01:26,919 --> 00:01:28,239
she wouldn't bend the rules

12
00:01:28,440 --> 00:01:29,440
to cover up for a suspect.

13
00:01:29,879 --> 00:01:30,639
Suspect?

14
00:01:31,239 --> 00:01:32,519
How did I become a suspect again?

15
00:01:32,720 --> 00:01:33,480
Gu Tiancheng,

16
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:35,839
stop beating around the bush

17
00:01:35,839 --> 00:01:37,480
and wasting both of our time, okay?

18
00:01:39,599 --> 00:01:40,639
I'll ask you one more time.

19
00:01:40,760 --> 00:01:42,279
Did you access the files?

20
00:01:42,800 --> 00:01:44,120
I had a reason.

21
00:01:44,319 --> 00:01:44,639
Here's the thing,

22
00:01:44,839 --> 00:01:45,839
I'll explain it to you one more time.

23
00:01:46,199 --> 00:01:48,040
I am the recipient of this heart.

24
00:01:48,639 --> 00:01:50,639
So I just wanted to know whose heart it was.

25
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:52,440
Can you put yourself in my shoes?

26
00:01:52,959 --> 00:01:54,800
If you received a heart out of nowhere,

27
00:01:55,160 --> 00:01:56,319
wouldn't you be curious too?

28
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:58,360
Wouldn't you want to know whose heart it is?

29
00:01:58,680 --> 00:01:59,800
So you're saying,

30
00:01:59,919 --> 00:02:01,279
because of your personal curiosity,

31
00:02:01,599 --> 00:02:02,559
you broke the law.

32
00:02:02,959 --> 00:02:04,639
Do you know you've violated the

33
00:02:04,639 --> 00:02:07,120
Tort Liability Law and invaded a citizen's privacy?

34
00:02:07,639 --> 00:02:08,080
I know.

35
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:08,960
So that means

36
00:02:09,199 --> 00:02:11,199
you knowingly broke the law.

37
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,000
Jiaqi

38
00:02:24,119 --> 00:02:25,360
Now that you know the truth,

39
00:02:26,720 --> 00:02:28,279
you finally understand my reasons, right?

40
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:29,880
When did you find out?

41
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:31,880
When I found out isn't important.

42
00:02:33,039 --> 00:02:34,559
What matters is that you know now.

43
00:02:34,880 --> 00:02:36,000
As a friend,

44
00:02:36,559 --> 00:02:38,000
I've fulfilled my obligation.

45
00:02:38,559 --> 00:02:39,960
You don't look too happy.

46
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:42,919
You look so listless.

47
00:02:45,080 --> 00:02:46,520
I did you such a huge favor.

48
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:48,119
How are you going to thank me?

49
00:02:49,399 --> 00:02:50,639
Why should I thank you?

50
00:02:51,119 --> 00:02:52,240
There's someone with bad intentions

51
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:53,679
hovering around you.

52
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:55,600
I kindly warned you

53
00:02:56,320 --> 00:02:57,759
so you could see his true colors.

54
00:02:59,839 --> 00:03:00,880
Such a huge favor,

55
00:03:02,039 --> 00:03:02,880
how will you repay it?

56
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:04,039
I did it for you,

57
00:03:04,039 --> 00:03:05,880
before your feelings for Gu Tiancheng deepened,

58
00:03:06,759 --> 00:03:07,880
to help you put a stop to it.

59
00:03:07,880 --> 00:03:09,240
Otherwise, how long would you be fooled?

60
00:03:10,679 --> 00:03:11,479
Do you know why

61
00:03:11,479 --> 00:03:12,440
you're so deeply attracted to him?

62
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:14,479
Even though from the very beginning,

63
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:16,440
his attitude towards you was terrible.

64
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:19,399
Why did you suddenly fall for him?

65
00:03:20,440 --> 00:03:22,080
I think it's because in Gu Tiancheng,

66
00:03:22,479 --> 00:03:23,759
you saw Du Zheng's shadow.

67
00:03:24,039 --> 00:03:25,080
Gu Tiancheng is Gu Tiancheng.

68
00:03:25,279 --> 00:03:26,039
Du Zheng is Du Zheng.

69
00:03:26,320 --> 00:03:27,800
They are two completely different individuals.

70
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,839
Just keep lying to yourself.

71
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:32,839
You just refuse to admit it.

72
00:03:33,119 --> 00:03:34,600
If you hadn't learned the truth today,

73
00:03:35,479 --> 00:03:37,199
would you have kept lying to yourself like this?

74
00:03:37,720 --> 00:03:39,479
Gu Tiancheng has been constantly showing you attention.

75
00:03:40,160 --> 00:03:41,479
Does he really like you,

76
00:03:41,880 --> 00:03:42,880
or is it because of Du Zheng's

77
00:03:42,880 --> 00:03:44,119
cellular memory of the heart

78
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:45,960
instinctively keeping him by your side?

79
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:48,399
If he hadn't received Du Zheng's heart,

80
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:50,520
would he still like you?

81
00:03:51,080 --> 00:03:52,240
Enough, stop talking.

82
00:03:53,039 --> 00:03:54,240
Does this have anything to do with you?

83
00:03:57,279 --> 00:03:58,240
Excuse me,

84
00:04:02,039 --> 00:04:03,000
when you said you wanted to investigate,

85
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:03,880
I told you

86
00:04:04,720 --> 00:04:06,039
it would be completely useless.

87
00:04:06,559 --> 00:04:07,360
And now look,

88
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:08,759
you got me

89
00:04:08,759 --> 00:04:10,039
almost thrown in jail.

90
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,479
We didn't accomplish anything,

91
00:04:13,639 --> 00:04:15,479
just a one-day tour of the police station.

92
00:04:17,239 --> 00:04:18,359
Did you call her?

93
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:21,119
Who?

94
00:04:21,519 --> 00:04:23,679
Didn't you ask Lin Jiaqi to go flower viewing today?

95
00:04:26,320 --> 00:04:27,160
I completely forgot.

96
00:04:27,440 --> 00:04:28,119
What do I do? What do I do?

97
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,640
I bet she's still waiting for you.

98
00:04:31,679 --> 00:04:32,160
Turn around.

99
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:33,920
Boss, why turn around?

100
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:34,880
We've already driven so far.

101
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:36,079
It's been a long day.

102
00:04:37,239 --> 00:04:37,880
Turn around.

103
00:04:38,399 --> 00:04:39,239
Okay, okay, okay.

104
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:40,239
Whatever you say.

105
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:41,399
I'll listen to you.

106
00:04:55,559 --> 00:04:56,359
Where did you go?

107
00:05:02,640 --> 00:05:04,119
Did you go flower viewing by yourself?

108
00:05:08,679 --> 00:05:09,880
I know I...

109
00:05:11,799 --> 00:05:12,839
Today, I...

110
00:05:13,559 --> 00:05:15,920
didn't show up or tell you in advance.

111
00:05:16,799 --> 00:05:18,200
What happened to you today?

112
00:05:21,359 --> 00:05:22,119
Qi Shuai got sick.

113
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:23,880
You know this kid,

114
00:05:23,880 --> 00:05:25,239
he's usually as strong as an ox.

115
00:05:25,679 --> 00:05:26,959
But he gets sick at critical moments.

116
00:05:27,440 --> 00:05:28,679
Is he better now?

117
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:31,920
I took him to see a doctor.

118
00:05:32,640 --> 00:05:34,239
He took some medicine and got a shot.

119
00:05:34,440 --> 00:05:35,480
He's fine now.

120
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:39,239
Please don't be mad.

121
00:05:39,239 --> 00:05:40,160
I know I should have

122
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:40,959
told you beforehand.

123
00:05:41,880 --> 00:05:43,519
But my phone happened to die.

124
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,399
To make it up to you,

125
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:48,320
let's go see a movie, okay?

126
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,440
I already bought the tickets.

127
00:05:51,399 --> 00:05:51,880
Let's go.

128
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:53,559
No need.

129
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:55,640
What's wrong?

130
00:05:56,799 --> 00:05:58,040
Stop being mad, okay?

131
00:05:58,839 --> 00:05:59,880
I don't feel very well.

132
00:05:59,959 --> 00:06:00,799
I want to go back first.

133
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,000
Let me check if you have a fever.

134
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:03,440
Don't touch me.

135
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:04,880
I'm begging you.

136
00:06:05,079 --> 00:06:06,000
I want to go home now.

137
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:06,920
I want to rest.

138
00:06:06,959 --> 00:06:08,079
I'm tired. It's been a long day.

139
00:06:08,079 --> 00:06:09,399
Can I just rest?

140
00:06:40,679 --> 00:06:41,320
Shihui.

141
00:06:41,320 --> 00:06:41,920
President Gu.

142
00:06:42,359 --> 00:06:43,239
Have you seen Director Lin?

143
00:06:43,760 --> 00:06:45,119
Sis Jiaqi didn't come in today.

144
00:06:46,959 --> 00:06:47,399
President Gu.

145
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:50,239
Sis Jiaqi is sick today.

146
00:06:50,559 --> 00:06:51,480
She said she needs to take a day off.

147
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:53,119
Sick?

148
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:56,640
Sis Jiaqi has never taken a sick day.

149
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:58,359
It seems pretty serious this time.

150
00:06:58,799 --> 00:07:00,760
We were talking about visiting her after work.

151
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:02,839
You two,

152
00:07:02,839 --> 00:07:03,720
no need to visit her tonight.

153
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:04,720
Get back to work.

154
00:07:10,640 --> 00:07:11,239
President Gu.

155
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:12,559
President Gu.

156
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,119
The people from Jincheng International are arriving soon.

157
00:07:15,119 --> 00:07:16,600
We can head to the factory now.

158
00:07:18,760 --> 00:07:19,320
Okay.

159
00:07:28,399 --> 00:07:29,040
Look.

160
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:30,760
Production is currently underway.

161
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:32,440
Once all the raw materials arrive,

162
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:33,600
the second batch can begin.

163
00:07:45,160 --> 00:07:45,760
Hello.

164
00:07:45,760 --> 00:07:46,279
This way, please.

165
00:07:46,279 --> 00:07:46,559
Okay.

166
00:07:46,559 --> 00:07:47,440
Let me continue the introduction.

167
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:48,359
Pick up the phone.

168
00:07:48,359 --> 00:07:49,839
President, what are you doing?

169
00:07:50,119 --> 00:07:51,600
You're really not yourself today.

170
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:53,119
The boss of this company

171
00:07:53,119 --> 00:07:54,720
looks at the person, not the project.

172
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:56,079
With your current mental state,

173
00:07:56,559 --> 00:07:57,279
what if something goes wrong?

174
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:58,720
All right, I know.

175
00:07:59,359 --> 00:08:00,239
So nagging.

176
00:08:08,519 --> 00:08:09,720
Your project documents,

177
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:11,320
we've reviewed them in detail.

178
00:08:12,119 --> 00:08:13,040
The company held a meeting

179
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:13,959
and studied them.

180
00:08:15,559 --> 00:08:17,200
We think your products

181
00:08:17,200 --> 00:08:18,920
have great development prospects.

182
00:08:19,440 --> 00:08:21,600
Then the quantity of products your company needs,

183
00:08:21,880 --> 00:08:22,559
roughly how much is it?

184
00:08:22,839 --> 00:08:23,640
First of all,

185
00:08:24,079 --> 00:08:24,959
let's say 100,000 units.

186
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:26,480
How many?

187
00:08:27,239 --> 00:08:28,399
100,000 units.

188
00:08:28,760 --> 00:08:29,320
Yes.

189
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:30,559
I wonder how this sounds.

190
00:08:31,279 --> 00:08:32,719
If you can provide us with

191
00:08:32,719 --> 00:08:34,039
a 20% advance payment,

192
00:08:34,799 --> 00:08:36,000
once the main raw materials arrive,

193
00:08:36,479 --> 00:08:38,080
we can immediately start the second batch of production.

194
00:08:38,359 --> 00:08:39,080
President Gu,

195
00:08:40,039 --> 00:08:41,880
you really know how to do business.

196
00:08:42,400 --> 00:08:43,919
Such a high advance payment,

197
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:46,280
I've never encountered it before.

198
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:48,840
But at this stage,

199
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:49,919
the problems our company is facing

200
00:08:49,919 --> 00:08:50,719
are just like this.

201
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:51,520
So,

202
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,119
I hope you can understand.

203
00:08:54,799 --> 00:08:55,479
All right.

204
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:59,719
I'll try to discuss it with the head office.

205
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:00,479
Okay.

206
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,799
Then I'll wait for your good news.

207
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,159
Pleasure doing business.

208
00:09:05,799 --> 00:09:06,320
Pleasure doing business.

209
00:09:07,679 --> 00:09:08,359
Pleasure doing business.

210
00:09:08,880 --> 00:09:09,520
I'll see you out.

211
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:18,640
What?

212
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:21,080
A 20% advance payment?

213
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:22,080
And paid in cash?

214
00:09:22,320 --> 00:09:22,760
Yes.

215
00:09:23,359 --> 00:09:24,880
They said they need funds

216
00:09:25,559 --> 00:09:27,119
to continue production.

217
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:30,559
Okay.

218
00:09:31,039 --> 00:09:32,119
Just do as they said.

219
00:09:32,679 --> 00:09:33,119
Old Wang,

220
00:09:33,799 --> 00:09:35,080
I'll have to trouble you to make another trip later

221
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:36,520
to help us deliver the money.

222
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:37,559
Okay.

223
00:09:37,799 --> 00:09:38,479
Old Wang,

224
00:09:38,599 --> 00:09:39,760
please step out for a moment.

225
00:09:47,679 --> 00:09:49,359
Feng Ziang, are you crazy?

226
00:09:49,719 --> 00:09:51,119
That's the company's money.

227
00:09:51,359 --> 00:09:52,359
Gu Tiancheng doesn't know

228
00:09:52,479 --> 00:09:54,080
that Jincheng International is a shell company.

229
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:56,119
We paid a 20% advance payment,

230
00:09:56,640 --> 00:09:57,960
so they definitely won't suspect anything.

231
00:09:58,280 --> 00:09:59,679
Instead, they'll start increasing production.

232
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:01,599
When their production is almost finished,

233
00:10:01,919 --> 00:10:03,200
we'll let Jincheng International go bankrupt.

234
00:10:03,520 --> 00:10:04,000
At that time,

235
00:10:04,359 --> 00:10:06,080
they'll have about 80,000 units of stranded goods.

236
00:10:06,719 --> 00:10:07,320
Think about it.

237
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:09,280
The loan for additional production,

238
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,479
plus the maturing bonds,

239
00:10:10,599 --> 00:10:11,200
this blow

240
00:10:11,559 --> 00:10:13,440
is enough to make Feimanchi completely unable to recover.

241
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:20,200
I hope so.

242
00:10:23,039 --> 00:10:23,880
Lin Jiaqi!

243
00:10:27,760 --> 00:10:29,000
Lin Jiaqi, are you in the room?

244
00:10:31,599 --> 00:10:32,239
In the middle of the night,

245
00:10:32,280 --> 00:10:33,080
what are you doing?

246
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:36,520
Ma'am,

247
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:37,880
are you the landlady?

248
00:10:38,159 --> 00:10:38,760
Yes.

249
00:10:39,719 --> 00:10:40,280
That's great.

250
00:10:41,599 --> 00:10:42,440
My good friend,

251
00:10:42,760 --> 00:10:43,400
Lin Jiaqi,

252
00:10:44,159 --> 00:10:45,159
she lives in this room.

253
00:10:45,599 --> 00:10:46,400
She might be sick.

254
00:10:46,799 --> 00:10:47,440
I'm worried.

255
00:10:47,719 --> 00:10:48,760
Do you have the key?

256
00:10:48,880 --> 00:10:50,239
Can you let me in to check on her?

257
00:10:50,599 --> 00:10:51,520
I'm afraid something happened to her.

258
00:10:52,840 --> 00:10:53,320
Okay.

259
00:10:58,359 --> 00:10:58,760
Go ahead.

260
00:10:58,760 --> 00:10:59,200
Thank you.

261
00:11:10,159 --> 00:11:10,799
You're awake.

262
00:11:12,239 --> 00:11:13,159
You're finally awake.

263
00:11:14,239 --> 00:11:15,280
Feeling any better now?

264
00:11:16,760 --> 00:11:17,760
How did you get in?

265
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:20,200
I knew you were sick.

266
00:11:20,880 --> 00:11:22,799
I rang the doorbell for ages, but no one answered.

267
00:11:23,880 --> 00:11:25,440
Then I happened to run into the landlady.

268
00:11:26,280 --> 00:11:26,840
She opened the door

269
00:11:26,840 --> 00:11:27,840
and let me in.

270
00:11:30,599 --> 00:11:31,400
Don't get up.

271
00:11:37,679 --> 00:11:38,400
Did you know?

272
00:11:39,080 --> 00:11:40,599
Your fever reached 39 degrees.

273
00:11:42,239 --> 00:11:42,799
After that,

274
00:11:43,039 --> 00:11:44,200
I got someone from a nearby clinic

275
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:45,559
to set up an IV drip for you,

276
00:11:46,039 --> 00:11:47,000
and give you a fever-reducing shot.

277
00:11:48,479 --> 00:11:49,760
Are you feeling any better now?

278
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:52,640
Are you hungry?

279
00:11:53,159 --> 00:11:54,320
Do you want me to make you some porridge?

280
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:03,039
Get out.

281
00:12:03,679 --> 00:12:04,400
I'm not leaving.

282
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:06,440
You still have a fever.

283
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:08,640
What if something happens tonight?

284
00:12:09,400 --> 00:12:10,840
I told you to get out, did you hear me?

285
00:12:11,919 --> 00:12:12,880
What's wrong with you?

286
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:17,000
Get out!

287
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:18,640
Alright then.

288
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:21,080
Get some good rest.

289
00:12:22,599 --> 00:12:23,239
Tomorrow,

290
00:12:24,840 --> 00:12:25,919
take another day off to rest.

291
00:12:26,799 --> 00:12:27,320
Oh, right.

292
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:28,679
I sorted out your medicine

293
00:12:28,799 --> 00:12:29,919
and put it on the table outside.

294
00:12:30,799 --> 00:12:31,840
Remember to take it.

295
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:34,039
If you feel unwell tonight,

296
00:12:34,640 --> 00:12:35,599
call me immediately.

297
00:12:38,679 --> 00:12:39,320
I'll be going now.

298
00:13:02,960 --> 00:13:04,679
Why didn't you go home last night?

299
00:13:04,960 --> 00:13:05,559
How do you know?

300
00:13:05,719 --> 00:13:06,880
I waited at your place for ages.

301
00:13:06,880 --> 00:13:08,000
I even fell asleep waiting.

302
00:13:09,520 --> 00:13:10,919
Did you go see Jiaqi?

303
00:13:10,919 --> 00:13:11,520
No.

304
00:13:11,799 --> 00:13:13,400
I just got back quite late.

305
00:13:14,239 --> 00:13:14,799
What time?

306
00:13:14,919 --> 00:13:15,880
Are you done?

307
00:13:16,719 --> 00:13:17,400
Tell me the truth.

308
00:13:17,400 --> 00:13:18,679
Am I the president, or are you?

309
00:13:22,760 --> 00:13:23,880
Good morning, President Gu.

310
00:13:25,880 --> 00:13:27,000
Why are you here so early?

311
00:13:27,640 --> 00:13:29,239
Did you sleep well last night?

312
00:13:29,599 --> 00:13:30,559
Are you still feeling unwell?

313
00:13:32,960 --> 00:13:33,760
I'm fine.

314
00:13:34,799 --> 00:13:36,320
Didn't I tell you to rest for a couple more days?

315
00:13:37,119 --> 00:13:38,200
Don't push yourself if you're tired.

316
00:13:39,520 --> 00:13:40,559
There's too much going on at the company.

317
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:41,840
I can't delay my work.

318
00:13:44,159 --> 00:13:45,440
I also need to go to the Industry and Commerce Bureau.

319
00:13:45,799 --> 00:13:47,039
If there's nothing else,

320
00:13:47,320 --> 00:13:47,960
I'll get going.

321
00:13:48,880 --> 00:13:49,400
Okay.

322
00:13:56,239 --> 00:13:57,239
Stop staring.

323
00:13:57,359 --> 00:13:58,880
She's already far away.

324
00:14:00,080 --> 00:14:02,599
Get to work.

325
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:05,119
You're not getting a single cent for your year-end bonus this year.

326
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:25,719
There's a

327
00:14:25,840 --> 00:14:27,080
watch with a strange pattern.

328
00:14:28,159 --> 00:14:29,159
The person wearing that watch

329
00:14:29,559 --> 00:14:30,599
is connected to this murder.

330
00:14:31,559 --> 00:14:32,679
I saw Feng Ziang today,

331
00:14:32,679 --> 00:14:33,840
and he was wearing that watch.

332
00:14:34,239 --> 00:14:35,400
In the substandard raw materials incident,

333
00:14:35,840 --> 00:14:37,280
Feng Ziang is the real culprit.

334
00:14:46,119 --> 00:14:46,840
Hello, Jiaqi.

335
00:14:47,159 --> 00:14:48,239
Are you free right now?

336
00:14:53,239 --> 00:14:54,239
Have you been waiting long?

337
00:14:54,719 --> 00:14:55,359
Not really.

338
00:14:56,080 --> 00:14:57,440
Waiter, I'll have a glass of orange juice.

339
00:14:57,599 --> 00:14:58,239
Okay.

340
00:14:59,320 --> 00:15:00,080
Jiaqi,

341
00:15:00,400 --> 00:15:01,520
I have something to ask you.

342
00:15:02,400 --> 00:15:02,719
Go ahead.

343
00:15:08,080 --> 00:15:09,080
This watch...

344
00:15:09,719 --> 00:15:10,520
Was it

345
00:15:10,960 --> 00:15:12,280
given to Feng Ziang by Du Zheng?

346
00:15:12,960 --> 00:15:13,640
Take a look.

347
00:15:13,919 --> 00:15:14,440
Yes.

348
00:15:14,960 --> 00:15:16,679
Although it was given in my name,

349
00:15:17,320 --> 00:15:18,640
Du Zheng bought it.

350
00:15:20,200 --> 00:15:21,039
At that time,

351
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:23,679
I became the chairman's secretary,

352
00:15:24,719 --> 00:15:27,119
and Ziang became the legal director.

353
00:15:27,440 --> 00:15:28,520
We agreed

354
00:15:29,039 --> 00:15:30,840
to give each other promotion gifts.

355
00:15:31,280 --> 00:15:33,400
But I was too busy then and forgot.

356
00:15:33,760 --> 00:15:34,840
Du Zheng bought it

357
00:15:35,039 --> 00:15:36,479
and gave it to Ziang in my name.

358
00:15:40,440 --> 00:15:41,479
So that means

359
00:15:42,039 --> 00:15:43,679
Feng Ziang doesn't know this watch

360
00:15:43,679 --> 00:15:44,880
was given by Du Zheng?

361
00:15:47,080 --> 00:15:48,239
Why are you suddenly asking this?

362
00:15:48,440 --> 00:15:49,520
It's been so long.

363
00:15:51,239 --> 00:15:51,840
It's nothing.

364
00:15:52,640 --> 00:15:54,559
I just want to buy an identical one.

365
00:15:59,799 --> 00:16:00,559
Jiaqi,

366
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:02,039
lately,

367
00:16:02,359 --> 00:16:04,119
is your relationship with Feng Ziang okay?

368
00:16:05,960 --> 00:16:06,799
Don't mention him.

369
00:16:14,000 --> 00:16:14,559
Yaoyao,

370
00:16:17,599 --> 00:16:18,599
actually,

371
00:16:20,479 --> 00:16:22,039
actually you were right before.

372
00:16:24,559 --> 00:16:25,559
I once

373
00:16:27,799 --> 00:16:29,119
had feelings for the president.

374
00:16:34,200 --> 00:16:35,239
What did I tell you?

375
00:16:35,479 --> 00:16:36,919
I knew Gu Tiancheng

376
00:16:36,919 --> 00:16:38,599
tried hard to win you over.

377
00:16:40,640 --> 00:16:42,320
But I know why I felt that way now.

378
00:16:42,880 --> 00:16:43,520
Why?

379
00:16:45,760 --> 00:16:46,599
Because...

380
00:16:50,200 --> 00:16:51,880
Because Gu Tiancheng's heart

381
00:16:53,159 --> 00:16:54,320
is Du Zheng's.

382
00:16:56,440 --> 00:16:57,479
Oh my god.

383
00:16:58,280 --> 00:16:59,479
Things like this actually happen?

384
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:03,599
I really don't know what to do.

385
00:17:05,359 --> 00:17:06,680
I was in Du Zheng's arms,

386
00:17:07,359 --> 00:17:08,880
listening to his heartbeat for so many years.

387
00:17:12,439 --> 00:17:13,719
But now his heart

388
00:17:13,719 --> 00:17:15,400
is actually inside Gu Tiancheng's body.

389
00:17:15,800 --> 00:17:17,560
Although I don't really like Gu Tiancheng either,

390
00:17:19,040 --> 00:17:20,280
as your good friend,

391
00:17:20,280 --> 00:17:21,599
I have to say something.

392
00:17:22,520 --> 00:17:23,400
Have you ever thought

393
00:17:24,119 --> 00:17:25,560
that maybe you're also at fault?

394
00:17:26,040 --> 00:17:27,719
From the very beginning, you didn't distinguish

395
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:29,280
between Du Zheng and Gu Tiancheng.

396
00:17:29,800 --> 00:17:31,680
That's why things have come to this.

397
00:17:32,439 --> 00:17:33,319
Yes.

398
00:17:34,760 --> 00:17:35,719
It's my fault.

399
00:17:38,439 --> 00:17:39,839
And because of my mistake,

400
00:17:41,319 --> 00:17:42,719
I hurt Gu Tiancheng.

401
00:17:44,359 --> 00:17:45,880
But even knowing this,

402
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:48,520
I still have to hurt him.

403
00:17:50,319 --> 00:17:52,000
Because I can't face him.

404
00:17:53,839 --> 00:17:54,479
No,

405
00:17:57,640 --> 00:17:59,239
I can't face Du Zheng.

406
00:18:02,479 --> 00:18:03,839
Since you already know,

407
00:18:04,920 --> 00:18:06,560
choosing to give up at this time,

408
00:18:07,160 --> 00:18:08,199
wouldn't it be better?

409
00:18:17,359 --> 00:18:18,000
Come in.

410
00:18:28,119 --> 00:18:28,680
President Gu.

411
00:18:28,880 --> 00:18:29,680
Did you need me for something?

412
00:18:34,239 --> 00:18:34,920
Have some coffee.

413
00:18:37,119 --> 00:18:37,800
Do you take sugar?

414
00:18:38,319 --> 00:18:40,000
If there's nothing else,

415
00:18:40,599 --> 00:18:41,719
I still have work to do.

416
00:18:43,160 --> 00:18:44,199
Why are you always avoiding me?

417
00:18:47,079 --> 00:18:47,640
I'm not.

418
00:18:47,920 --> 00:18:48,640
You are.

419
00:18:53,040 --> 00:18:54,439
Are you still mad at me?

420
00:18:54,880 --> 00:18:55,640
Then right here, right now,

421
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:57,000
let me sincerely apologize to you, okay?

422
00:19:00,560 --> 00:19:02,040
That wasn't a big deal.

423
00:19:03,359 --> 00:19:03,920
It's fine.

424
00:19:04,560 --> 00:19:05,920
You're definitely still mad at me.

425
00:19:06,760 --> 00:19:07,280
Jiaqi.

426
00:19:07,640 --> 00:19:08,839
I shouldn't have stood you up that day.

427
00:19:08,959 --> 00:19:10,479
I didn't even let you know beforehand.

428
00:19:10,760 --> 00:19:11,880
But I really didn't do it on purpose.

429
00:19:11,880 --> 00:19:13,119
Please believe me, okay?

430
00:19:14,280 --> 00:19:15,680
I already said it's fine.

431
00:19:16,400 --> 00:19:17,079
Jiaqi.

432
00:19:17,719 --> 00:19:18,760
What do you want me to do

433
00:19:19,000 --> 00:19:19,839
so you can forgive me?

434
00:19:20,719 --> 00:19:21,520
As long as you name it,

435
00:19:21,839 --> 00:19:22,520
I'll definitely do it.

436
00:19:27,640 --> 00:19:28,359
Okay.

437
00:19:29,599 --> 00:19:30,599
Then I'll take that as a promise.

438
00:19:30,760 --> 00:19:31,239
Okay.

439
00:19:37,760 --> 00:19:38,800
Take a look at this.

440
00:19:41,640 --> 00:19:43,119
Resignation letter?

441
00:19:44,479 --> 00:19:45,319
What is this about?

442
00:19:48,239 --> 00:19:49,560
All I did was stand you up.

443
00:19:49,560 --> 00:19:50,800
Just this once.

444
00:19:50,800 --> 00:19:52,479
Did I make such a grave mistake?

445
00:19:53,160 --> 00:19:54,079
If you're angry,

446
00:19:54,959 --> 00:19:56,359
if you hate me or despise me,

447
00:19:56,640 --> 00:19:57,560
you can scold me or hit me.

448
00:19:57,560 --> 00:19:58,839
Just take it out on me.

449
00:19:59,319 --> 00:20:01,199
Don't do this, okay, Lin Jiaqi?

450
00:20:01,839 --> 00:20:03,520
It's really agonizing for me to keep guessing like this.

451
00:20:03,520 --> 00:20:04,119
President Gu.

452
00:20:06,959 --> 00:20:08,160
I'm telling the truth.

453
00:20:11,680 --> 00:20:13,160
The company's situation has improved.

454
00:20:14,000 --> 00:20:15,119
I want to take a break.

455
00:20:16,439 --> 00:20:17,079
Sure.

456
00:20:17,719 --> 00:20:18,520
Then I'll give you some time off.

457
00:20:18,599 --> 00:20:20,160
You can just take a paid leave, right?

458
00:20:22,079 --> 00:20:23,160
I want to rest completely.

459
00:20:23,400 --> 00:20:24,680
I don't want any lingering ties.

460
00:20:27,800 --> 00:20:28,599
Jiaqi.

461
00:20:29,880 --> 00:20:31,560
Didn't you say you'd always stay by my side?

462
00:20:32,479 --> 00:20:33,640
It's all because of you

463
00:20:33,640 --> 00:20:34,719
that I've held on until today.

464
00:20:36,199 --> 00:20:37,280
That's enough, President Gu.

465
00:20:38,839 --> 00:20:40,319
I've already spoken with HR.

466
00:20:40,760 --> 00:20:42,560
I'll finish the handover in the next two days.

467
00:20:45,199 --> 00:20:45,800
I'm sorry.

468
00:20:55,520 --> 00:20:56,800
It seems that with Jincheng International,

469
00:20:57,079 --> 00:20:58,239
increasing the advance payment was right.

470
00:20:59,119 --> 00:21:00,319
Now Thailand has started ordering too.

471
00:21:01,319 --> 00:21:01,880
Really?

472
00:21:02,280 --> 00:21:03,520
That's a double blessing.

473
00:21:04,000 --> 00:21:05,800
Thailand ordered 100,000 pieces,

474
00:21:05,800 --> 00:21:06,920
and Vietnam ordered 100,000 pieces.

475
00:21:07,520 --> 00:21:08,560
That's 200,000 in total.

476
00:21:09,160 --> 00:21:09,520
Then...

477
00:21:09,800 --> 00:21:11,239
Then all our problems are solved.

478
00:21:11,959 --> 00:21:13,439
Make sure to confirm the meeting times.

479
00:21:13,719 --> 00:21:15,199
It's Tuesday and Wednesday of the week after next.

480
00:21:15,199 --> 00:21:16,079
I've marked them all for you.

481
00:21:16,079 --> 00:21:17,079
Please don't forget.

482
00:21:17,719 --> 00:21:18,199
Oh, right.

483
00:21:19,359 --> 00:21:21,640
This book is about heart-healthy foods.

484
00:21:21,839 --> 00:21:23,079
Pay more attention to it.

485
00:21:23,439 --> 00:21:24,719
Sis Jiaqi, are you serious?

486
00:21:24,719 --> 00:21:25,920
Are you really leaving?

487
00:21:25,920 --> 00:21:26,719
Of course I am.

488
00:21:27,119 --> 00:21:28,000
Only if I resign

489
00:21:28,199 --> 00:21:30,000
can you take my position, Weiwei.

490
00:21:30,239 --> 00:21:31,079
Sis Jiaqi...

491
00:21:32,439 --> 00:21:33,160
Jiaqi.

492
00:21:34,319 --> 00:21:35,040
Hello.

493
00:21:35,479 --> 00:21:36,640
May I ask if you are

494
00:21:38,400 --> 00:21:39,239
Detective Tan?

495
00:21:46,680 --> 00:21:47,959
I'm with Lin Jiaqi right now

496
00:21:47,959 --> 00:21:49,359
at the cafe downstairs from the company.

497
00:21:49,479 --> 00:21:50,359
Do you want to come over?

498
00:21:57,400 --> 00:21:57,959
Ziang.

499
00:21:58,239 --> 00:21:59,119
Over here.

500
00:22:00,560 --> 00:22:01,199
Jiaqi.

501
00:22:01,199 --> 00:22:02,119
I asked him to come.

502
00:22:03,400 --> 00:22:03,880
Jiaqi,

503
00:22:04,800 --> 00:22:06,000
why are you with Brother Tan?

504
00:22:07,199 --> 00:22:08,119
Detective Tan said

505
00:22:08,119 --> 00:22:10,000
he wanted to talk to me about the substandard materials.

506
00:22:10,800 --> 00:22:11,359
Jiaqi,

507
00:22:11,640 --> 00:22:12,280
look at you.

508
00:22:12,719 --> 00:22:14,239
Why are you being so polite to me?

509
00:22:14,520 --> 00:22:16,239
We used to work in the same company.

510
00:22:16,319 --> 00:22:17,640
You even used to call me Uncle.

511
00:22:18,640 --> 00:22:20,479
Even though I'm not at that company anymore,

512
00:22:20,760 --> 00:22:22,280
as I retired a long time ago.

513
00:22:23,359 --> 00:22:24,280
Then can we talk about

514
00:22:24,839 --> 00:22:26,479
the substandard materials now?

515
00:22:27,119 --> 00:22:27,839
About this matter,

516
00:22:28,239 --> 00:22:29,359
let's go to my office to talk.

517
00:22:29,880 --> 00:22:30,520
It'll be quieter.

518
00:22:31,199 --> 00:22:32,280
Look at all these people coming and going.

519
00:22:32,880 --> 00:22:33,560
There are so many people.

520
00:22:33,839 --> 00:22:34,319
No,

521
00:22:34,560 --> 00:22:35,319
well,

522
00:22:35,520 --> 00:22:36,800
the office is so stuffy.

523
00:22:37,520 --> 00:22:38,280
Whatever it is,

524
00:22:38,599 --> 00:22:39,560
let's just talk about it here.

525
00:22:40,439 --> 00:22:41,079
Brother Tan.

526
00:22:43,719 --> 00:22:44,280
Jiaqi,

527
00:22:44,839 --> 00:22:45,640
let me tell you.

528
00:22:46,079 --> 00:22:48,280
As a suspect for those substandard materials,

529
00:22:48,800 --> 00:22:49,839
I've long been cleared.

530
00:22:50,319 --> 00:22:51,400
The police said I'm fine.

531
00:22:52,040 --> 00:22:53,119
But these people,

532
00:22:53,599 --> 00:22:55,000
they still suspect me.

533
00:22:55,280 --> 00:22:56,880
Do you know how wronged I feel?

534
00:22:57,079 --> 00:22:58,319
If you are innocent,

535
00:22:58,520 --> 00:22:59,560
don't worry too much.

536
00:22:59,959 --> 00:23:01,319
The truth will come out one day.

537
00:23:01,800 --> 00:23:02,439
Oh, right.

538
00:23:03,199 --> 00:23:03,920
Also,

539
00:23:04,839 --> 00:23:05,680
about Du Zheng...

540
00:23:06,680 --> 00:23:07,880
When his funeral was held,

541
00:23:11,160 --> 00:23:11,800
I...

542
00:23:12,280 --> 00:23:13,280
I'm really sorry

543
00:23:14,119 --> 00:23:15,040
that I couldn't make it.

544
00:23:18,319 --> 00:23:19,040
It's fine.

545
00:23:19,680 --> 00:23:20,719
If you have time,

546
00:23:21,239 --> 00:23:22,800
just go visit his grave.
